	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64137942"><p>What a shitty and inaccurate headline, how about <i>Capitalism, You Have Blood on Your Hands!</i> or <i>Meta, You Have Blood on Your Hands!</i> or <i>Greedy Foolish Billionaires, You Have Blood on Your Hands!</i> instead?</p></div>
	</div>

